text: Kiki Bertens and Johanna Larsson were the defending champions, but lost in the quarterfinals to Andreea Mitu and Alicja Rosolska. Mitu and Rosolska went on to win the title, defeating Lesley Kerkhove and Lidziya Marozava in the final, 6–3, 7–5. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Swedish Open - Doubles 2016 Women's Doubles Category:2016 in Swedish women's sport
title: 2016 Swedish Open – Women's Doubles
